Class Designation

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.khalsa_ji.ems.Designation

  • @Entity
public class Designation
extends java.lang.Object
    The class Designation defines some useful properties for designations(Job titles) in any organisation, methods to play around with those defined properties and also acts as a database entity.
